<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>CorpTrain - Learning Platform</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/4.1.1/animate.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@400;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-red: #b00000;
            --dark-maroon: #8b0000;
            --accent-yellow: #ffd700;
            --light-grey: #f8f9fa;
            --white-color: #ffffff;
            --black-color: #000000;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
            background-color: var(--light-grey);
            font-size: 18px;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .navbar {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--dark-maroon), var(--primary-red));
            border-radius: 0 0 20px 20px;
        }

        .navbar-brand, .nav-link {
            color: var(--white-color) !important;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            transition: color 0.3s ease-in-out, text-shadow 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }

            .nav-link:hover {
                color: var(--accent-yellow) !important;
                text-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--accent-yellow), 0 0 15px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.5); /* Subtle glow on hover */
            }

        .hero-section {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #990000, #cc0000);
            color: var(--white-color);
            padding: 160px 20px 140px;
            border-radius: 0 0 40px 40px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

            .hero-section h1 {
                font-size: 4.5rem;
                font-weight: 900;
                color: var(--white-color); /* Ensure text color is white */
                /* Reduced glow effect for "Selamat Datang" */
                text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6), /* Softer white glow */
                0 0 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); /* Clearer, subtle black shadow */
                transition: all 0.5s ease-in-out;
            }
                /* Animation for H1 on load, can be combined with previous animate__fadeInUp */
                .hero-section h1.animate__animated.animate__fadeInUp {
                    animation-duration: 1.5s; /* Make animation a bit longer */
                }

            .hero-section::after {
                content: "";
                position: absolute;
                top: 0;
                left: 0;
                width: 100%;
                height: 100%;
                background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.2) 0%, transparent 70%);
                animation: pulse 5s infinite;
            }

            .hero-section p {
                font-size: 1.4rem;
                max-width: 900px;
                margin: 20px auto;
            }

        .section {
            padding: 100px 20px;
            border-radius: 40px;
        }

            .section h2 {
                font-weight: 900;
                font-size: 2.8rem;
                margin-bottom: 30px;
                position: relative;
                display: inline-block; /* Essential for text-shadow and underline */
                color: var(--primary-red); /* Base color for the text */
                text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.2), /* Subtle shadow for depth */
                0 0 10px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.4); /* Soft yellow glow */
                transition: text-shadow 0.3s ease-in-out;
                text-align: center; /* Pastikan judul di tengah */
                width: 100%; /* Agar inline-block tetap mengambil lebar penuh container untuk center */
            }

                /* Animated Underline for .section h2 */
                .section h2::after {
                    content: '';
                    position: absolute;
                    left: 50%;
                    transform: translateX(-50%);
                    bottom: -10px;
                    width: 0;
                    height: 5px;
                    background: var(--accent-yellow);
                    border-radius: 5px;
                    transition: width 0.4s ease-out;
                }

            .section:hover h2::after {
                width: 80px;
            }

            .section p {
                font-size: 1.25rem;
            }

        .about-box {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--white-color), #f0f0f0);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            border-radius: 25px;
            padding: 50px;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease forwards;
        }

        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 60px;
            color: var(--primary-red);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }

        .feature-box:hover .feature-icon {
            transform: scale(1.1); /* Icon slightly scales up on hover */
        }

        .feature-box {
            background: var(--white-color);
            padding: 30px 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease, background 0.3s ease;
        }

            .feature-box:hover {
                transform: translateY(-10px);
                box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
                background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #fffdfd, #f7f7f7); /* Subtle lighter background on hover */
            }

        .section-bg-red {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #b00028, #7c001b);
            color: var(--white-color);
            border-radius: 40px;
        }

            .section-bg-red h2 {
                color: var(--white-color); /* Ensure text color is white for this section */
                text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6), /* Softer white glow */
                0 0 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); /* Clearer, subtle black shadow */
                transition: text-shadow 0.3s ease-in-out;
                text-align: center; /* Pastikan judul di tengah */
                width: 100%; /* Agar inline-block tetap mengambil lebar penuh container untuk center */
            }

                .section-bg-red h2::after {
                    background: var(--accent-yellow); /* Underline becomes yellow on red background */
                    transition: width 0.4s ease-out;
                }

            .section-bg-red:hover h2::after {
                width: 80px;
            }


        .btn-danger {
            background-color: var(--primary-red);
            border-color: var(--primary-red);
            border-radius: 30px;
            padding: 14px 36px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
            color: var(--white-color); /* Pastikan teks tombol bahaya tetap putih */
        }

            .btn-danger:hover {
                background-color: var(--dark-maroon);
                border-color: var(--dark-maroon);
                transform: translateY(-3px);
                box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            }

        .btn-light {
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
            color: var(--white-color) !important; /* Mengembalikan warna teks tombol Login menjadi putih */
            background-color: transparent; /* Atau atur sesuai keinginan, ini untuk transparansi */
            border: 1px solid var(--white-color); /* Tambahkan border putih agar terlihat */
        }

            .btn-light:hover {
                transform: translateY(-3px);
                box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
                color: var(--accent-yellow) !important; /* Teks kuning saat hover */
                border-color: var(--accent-yellow); /* Border kuning saat hover */
            }


        .footer-text {
            padding: 30px 0;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #666;
            text-align: left;
            margin-left: 20px;
        }

        hr {
            display: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark fixed-top shadow animate__animated animate__fadeInDown">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold" href="#">CorpTrain</a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#about">Tentang</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#features">Fitur</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#dashboard">Dashboard</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link btn btn-light px-3 ms-2" href="/Account/Login">Login</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="hero-section animate__animated animate__fadeIn">
        <div class="container position-relative">
            <h1 class="animate__animated animate__fadeInUp">Selamat Datang di CorpTrain</h1>
            <p class="animate__animated animate__fadeInUp animate__delay-1s">
                Platform pembelajaran internal Weatherford yang dirancang untuk menyajikan pelatihan teknis, keselamatan, dan pengembangan kompetensi karyawan secara modern dan efisien.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="about" class="section bg-white animate__animated animate__fadeInUp">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="text-center mb-5">Tentang CorpTrain</h2>
            <div class="about-box">
                <p class="text-center">
                    CorpTrain adalah solusi pembelajaran digital internal dari Weatherford yang mengintegrasikan modul pelatihan teknis, manajemen keselamatan, dan pengembangan pribadi.
                    Dengan tampilan modern dan fitur lengkap, CorpTrain membantu perusahaan dalam memastikan setiap karyawan memiliki akses terhadap pengetahuan dan pelatihan berkualitas tinggi
                    sesuai dengan standar global industri energi.
                </p>
                <p class="text-center mt-3">
                    Mengoptimalkan Potensi Karyawan Anda dengan Pembelajaran Berkelas Dunia. CorpTrain menyatukan teknologi teruji dengan digitalisasi canggih untuk memberikan akses
                    berkelanjutan pada pelatihan berkualitas tinggi, memastikan kompetensi dan kesiapan menghadapi tantangan energi masa depan.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="features" class="section bg-light animate__animated animate__fadeInUp">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="text-center mb-5">Fitur Unggulan</h2>
            <div class="row text-center mt-4">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="feature-box">
                        <div class="feature-icon mb-3">📁</div>
                        <h5 class="fw-bold">Kelola Materi</h5>
                        <p>Admin dapat menambahkan modul pelatihan berupa PDF, video, dokumen teks, serta konten multimedia lainnya.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="feature-box">
                        <div class="feature-icon mb-3">📊</div>
                        <h5 class="fw-bold">Monitoring & Evaluasi</h5>
                        <p>Pelaporan progres pembelajaran dan evaluasi berbasis kuis serta penilaian kinerja langsung secara real-time.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="feature-box">
                        <div class="feature-icon mb-3">🎓</div>
                        <h5 class="fw-bold">Sertifikat Otomatis</h5>
                        <p>Peserta dapat menerima sertifikat digital otomatis setelah menyelesaikan pelatihan dan evaluasi.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="dashboard" class="section section-bg-red animate__animated animate__fadeInUp">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="text-center">Dashboard Pelatihan</h2>
            <p class="text-center w-75 mx-auto">
                Platform terintegrasi untuk akses materi pelatihan, memantau perkembangan, berinteraksi dengan instruktur, dan mengunduh sertifikat.
                Dashboard juga menyediakan pelaporan akurat untuk pemantauan HR dan manajemen.
            </p>
            <div class="text-center mt-4">
                <a href="/Account/Login" class="btn btn-light btn-lg">Masuk Sekarang</a>

                @if (ViewBag.Role == "Admin")
                {
                    <a href="/Training/Create" class="btn btn-danger btn-lg ms-2">Tambah Pelatihan</a>
                }
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="footer-text">
        &copy; 2025 CorpTrain - Project
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>